#: data/io.github.quodlibet.ExFalso.appdata.xml.in:18
msgid ""
"Ex Falso is a tag editor with the same tag editing interface as Quod Libet. "
"It lets you display and edit any tags you want in the file, for all the file "
"formats it supports."
msgstr ""
"Ex Falso ແມ່ນຕົວແກ້ໄຂແທັກທີ່ມີໜ້າຕາຄືກັບ Quod Libet. ມັນຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າສະແດງ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂແທັກຕ່າງໆໃນໄ"
"ຟລ໌ໄດ້ທຸກຮູບແບບທີ່ຮອງຮັບ."

#: data/io.github.quodlibet.ExFalso.appdata.xml.in:23
#: data/io.github.quodlibet.QuodLibet.appdata.xml.in:25
msgid ""
"Supported file formats include Ogg Vorbis/Opus/Speex/FLAC, MP3, FLAC, MOD/XM/"
"IT, Musepack, Wavpack, MPEG-4 AAC, Monkeys Audio, WMA, SPC, MIDI."
msgstr ""
"ຮູບແບບໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຮອງຮັບລວມມີ Ogg Vorbis/Opus/Speex/FLAC, MP3, FLAC, MOD/XM/IT, "
"Musepack, Wavpack, MPEG-4 AAC, Monkeys Audio, WMA, SPC, MIDI."

#: data/io.github.quodlibet.ExFalso.appdata.xml.in:33
msgid "Tag editing interface"
msgstr "ໜ້າຕາການແກ້ໄຂແທັກ"

#: data/io.github.quodlibet.QuodLibet.appdata.xml.in:19
msgid ""
"Quod Libet is a music management program. It provides several different ways "
"to view your audio library, as well as support for Internet radio and audio "
"feeds. It has extremely flexible metadata tag editing and searching "
"capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Quod Libet ແມ່ນໂປຣແກຣມຈັດການເພງ. ມັນມີຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການເບິ່ງຄັງເພງຂອງທ່ານ, ລວມທັງຮອງຮັບວິທະຍຸອິນເ"
"ຕີເນັດ ແລະ audio feeds. ມັນມີຄວາມສາມາດໃນການແກ້ໄຂແທັກ ແລະ ຄົ້ນຫາທີ່ຢືດຢຸ່ນທີ່ສຸດ."

#: data/io.github.quodlibet.QuodLibet.appdata.xml.in:35
msgid "Album list view"
msgstr "ມຸມມອງລາຍການອະລະບັ້ມ"

